NEW TIMES EDITION IN VENTURA COUNTY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The Times this week began publication of a daily Ventura County Edition with 
local news and advertising in Part B seven days a week. A weekly section called 
Ventura County Life will appear Thursday. 
</P>
