<HEADLINE>
<P>
TO THESE FANS, NCAA MEANS NO CLUE AT ALL 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
I am appalled by the audacity of the NCAA in its refusal to grant Cal State 
Long Beach basketball a berth in the postseason tournament. 
</P>
<P>
On one hand, these deities harass numerous coaches and their programs for 
archaic infractions, yet on the other hand, the NCAA cozies up to CBS and 
blames their subsequent malfeasance on the late timing of the final Big West 
match. 
</P>
<P>
The officials of the NCAA should be subject to the same scrutiny and virulent 
judgment that they parcel out -- and heading the inquisition should be Jerry 
Tarkanian, Neil McCarthy and Joe Harrington. I'm sure those three gentlemen 
would not be at a loss to locate transgressions of the accused. 
</P>
<P>
LENORE HAYES 
</P>
<P>
Long Beach 
</P>
</TEXT>
