Camarillo d. Thousand Oaks, 15-4, 15-6, 15-7 -- Outside hitter Matt Brimigion 
scored 15 points -- including a school-record four aces -- in 20 services to 
lead the Scorpions in a nonleague match at home. Craig Cornelius had 10 kills 
and Chris Sampson had 26 assists for Camarillo (3-3). 
</P>
<P>
Chaminade d. Campbell Hall, 16-14, 15-8, 7-15, 15-13 -- Rody Alvar had 22 kills 
and Lars Johnson added 17 for Chaminade (4-3) in a nonleague match at 
Chaminade. 
