<HEADLINE>
<P>
ORANGE COUNTY EARNINGS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Tricare Inc.: The Santa Ana occupational health care services company said 
earnings for its fiscal 1990 third quarter increased 23% to $319,000 from 
$259,000 for the corresponding period in 1989. 
</P>
<P>
Revenue for the quarter ended Feb. 28 rose 16% to $5 million from $4.3 million. 
</P>
<P>
For the first nine months of fiscal 1990, net income was $1.1 million, 21% 
higher than the $892,000 posted a year earlier. Revenue rose 17% to $14.9 
million from $12.8 million. 
</P>
