SERVICE FOR HARMON SET FOR MONDAY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
A Mass for Tom Harmon, who died of a heart attack Thursday, will be celebrated 
at St. Paul the Apostle Catholic Church, 10750 Ohio Ave., Monday at 4 p.m. 
</P>
